                    "subtype": "activation",
                    "name": "Activate",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "effect": "You pull a strap near the shield\u2019s enarmes to create a makeshift shelter that unfolds over the next minute. The shield becomes a pup tent until you spend another minute collapsing it. Within the tent is a satchel that holds 1 Bulk of rations and replenishes every week.",
